<DOC><DOCNO>  ZF108-711-142  </DOCNO><DOCID>08 711 142.andM;</DOCID><JOURNAL>PC Week  August 6 1990 v7 n31 p32(1)* Full Text COPYRIGHT Ziff-Davis Publishing Co. 1990.andM;</JOURNAL><TITLE>Adobe doubles speed of Mac font scaler. (Adobe Systems Inc.'s TypeManager 2.0 and Type Set 3 printer software) (productannouncement)</TITLE><AUTHOR>Picarille, Lisa.andM;</AUTHOR><DESCRIPT>Company:   Adobe Systems Inc. (product introduction).andO;Ticker:    ADBE.andO;Product:   Type Manager 2.0 (Printer software) (product enhancement)Adobe Type Set 3 (Computer font) (product introduction).andO;Topic:     EnhancementsPrinter SoftwarePerformance Improvement.andM;</DESCRIPT><TEXT>By Lisa PicarilleandM;Adobe Systems Inc. this week will begin shipping a faster version of itsAdobe Type Manager (ATM) font-scaling software for the Macintosh that aidsusers in loading fixed sizes of type.andM;ATM 2.0 allows users to generate matching screen and printer fonts twice asfast as did ATM 1.2, according to company officials in Mountain View, Calif.andM;&quot;The speed on the large-sized type is significantly faster, which makes itmuch more useful,&quot; said Doug Evans, an ATM 2.0 beta tester and vice presidentof PDR Computer Impressions Inc., a prepress/typography firm in New York.andO;&quot;Now we don't have to turn it off because it is too slow.&quot;andM;The program also includes a utility called Font Porter that allows users toinstall pregenerated bit-mapped fonts simply by dragging the Suitcase filesinto the Mac's System Folder, the officials said.andP;  This alleviates theproblems users encounter when installing fixed-size fonts through the Mac'sFont/DA Mover desk accessory, they added.andM;ATM 2.0 is priced at $99; registered users can upgrade for $20.andM;Adobe will also begin shipping this week a new type package for both the Macand PC called Adobe Type Set 3.andP;  The $198 package contains 11 populartypefaces, including versions of Adobe Garamond, Helvetica and Tekton.andP;  Adobecan be reached at (800) 83-FONTS.andO;</TEXT></DOC>